OL,3,CWes Streeting: BMA's plan for resident
OL,4,Cdoctor strike is 'unconscionable'
OL,6,FSpeaking to the Health and Social Care
OL,7,FCommittee, Streeting decried the BMA's
OL,8,Fadvice to resident doctors not to tell
OL,9,Ftheir employers if they were planning
OL,10,Fto take part in industrial action.
OL,12,F"Now, I might not agree with the BMA
OL,13,Fstrike action, but I do accept they
OL,14,Fhave a right to strike," said
OL,15,FStreeting.
OL,17,F"I do accept they follow the rules in
OL,18,Forder to go on strike.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
