OL,3,CWes Streeting: BMA's plan for resident
OL,4,Cdoctor strike is 'unconscionable'
OL,6,F"What I cannot fathom is how any
OL,7,Fdoctor in good conscience would make
OL,8,Fit harder for managers to make sure we
OL,9,Fhave safe staffing levels.
OL,11,F"So I just think the sort of the BMA's
OL,12,Fapproach to this from start to finish
OL,13,Fhas been completely wrong.
OL,15,F"The idea that doctors would go on
OL,16,Fstrike without informing their
OL,17,Femployer, not allowing planning for
OL,18,Fsafe staffing, I think, is
OL,19,Funconscionable, and I would urge
OL,20,Fresident doctors who are taking part
OL,21,Fin strike actions: do the right thing."
