OL,6,F"This is fundamental to the rights of
OL,7,Fworkers to protect their ability to
OL,8,Ftake industrial action. Our approach
OL,9,Fhas not changed since the last round
OL,10,Fof strike action, and we did not
OL,11,Freceive this response from the
OL,12,Fprevious government.
OL,14,F"We also remind employers that even
OL,15,Fthose doctors who inform hospitals
OL,16,Fthey intend not to strike can change
OL,17,Ftheir mind. The safe option is always
OL,18,Fto assume resident doctors are
OL,19,Fstriking, and plan accordingly.
