OL,3,CWes Streeting: BMA's plan for resident
OL,4,Cdoctor strike is 'unconscionable'
OL,6,F"We will work with NHS England to
OL,7,Fensure that strike action is safe for
OL,8,Fpatients. In previous rounds we were
OL,9,Fquick to act in the interests of
OL,10,Fpatient safety through our derogations
OL,11,Fprocess. We believe the evidence shows
OL,12,Fwe can strike safely.
OL,14,F"If NHS England wish to raise new
OL,15,Fconcerns about the derogations process
OL,16,Fthat has previously functioned well
OL,17,Fthey will need to discuss this with us
OL,18,Furgently."
