OL,6,FConcerns have also been raised about
OL,7,Fpossible strike action in other areas
OL,8,Fof the NHS, with reports that nurses
OL,9,Fcould also consider strike action.
OL,11,FThe Royal College of Nursing (RCN)
OL,12,Fpublished research on Monday claiming
OL,13,Fnurses' pay is #8,000 lower than if
OL,14,Fwages had kept up with inflation since
OL,15,F2010.
OL,17,FThe RCN said its analysis showed that
OL,18,Fnurses' pay has been "severely eroded"
OL,19,Fover the past years, especially for
OL,20,Fjunior staff.
