OL,6,FResident doctors' (formerly known as
OL,7,F'junior doctors') ultimate goal is for
OL,8,F"full pay restoration," a term they
OL,9,Fuse to refer to the erosion in real
OL,10,Fterms of their salary since 2008 after
OL,11,Fmultiple below inflation payrises.
OL,13,FThe union has said that resident
OL,14,Fdoctors need a pay uplift of 29.2% to
OL,15,Freverse "pay erosion" since 2008.
OL,17,FIn September, BMA members voted to
OL,18,Faccept a government pay deal worth
OL,19,F22.3% on average over two years.
